      "content": "but those small steps feel so meaningless though. like, what is the point of saving a few plastic bags or planting a tree when the entire ecosystem is collapsing? it just feels like we're rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. it's actually exhausting trying to pretend there's a way out when everything is clearly just doomed.",
