    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see the logic in it. its hard to want to live a whole life, work a job, and deal with all the struggle, just to watch everything i care about get destroyed anyway. it feels like we're just being forced to participate in a slow-motion tragedy. sometimes it feels more like a mercy to just skip the whole thing and be done with it. like, why stay for the funeral?",
